            "  Topic 2: woman, sex, life, want, love, feel, hate, relationship, way, never\n",
            "  Topic 3: incels, incel, female, woman, normies, sub, normie, men, male, white\n",
            "  Topic 4: woman, look, guy, men, chad, ugly, girl, attractive, face, looking\n",
            "  Topic 5: year, old, virgin, girl, date, please, year old, guy, age, message\n",
